{"tid":1133741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇亞雷斯帶領利物浦作客大炒巴塞隆拿","createTime":"2019-05-01T09:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T13:37:21.000Z","uid":3454,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"64917c0d5d28a7d377c140b3872cce6ef0efb8c2","tid":1133741,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/5/255/22055249255/22054468033_583x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F5%2F255%2F22055249255%2F22054468033_583x420.jpg&h=e0b1493f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=776ccaa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】蘇亞雷斯於周五世盃8強硬撼法國前，與隊友一起打機減壓，更反映了他對前球會利物浦念念不忘。<br />\n<br />\n烏拉圭周五將會在世界盃8強對戰法國，大戰當前壓力在所難免，然而，烏拉圭前鋒蘇亞雷斯（Luis Suarez）就自有減壓之道。<br />\n<br />\n從網上一段instagram片段顯示，「阿蘇」於大戰法國前選擇的減壓方式，是跟後備門將隊友馬田甘賓拿一起玩電玩足球遊戲《FIFA 18》，遊戲中蘇亞雷斯竟然大膽倒戈，以前東家利物浦對戰甘賓拿所選的巴塞隆拿，只見阿蘇全程玩得開心，完全沒有因為大戰當前而影響心情，亦顯出他對舊東家念念不忘。<br />\n<br />\n回說兩人於遊戲中的戰況，蘇亞雷斯明顯對利物浦的實力仍然瞭如指掌，在穆罕默德沙拿和佐敦軒達臣密密建功下，其領軍的利記竟以8:2大炒巴塞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea33ed1d35340b71ca65d442ba102b32f00f1321","tid":1133741,"uid":177215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"打飛機post"},{"pid":"332f08c501b524ba5c0ce8e0710c9093d5cd1f10","tid":1133741,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"蘇亞雷斯、古天奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436530e5173204f729592c19e149826903eb9b55","tid":1133741,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea33ed1d35340b71ca65d442ba102b32f00f1321","tid":1133741,"uid":177215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:58:21.000Z","